reviewText: Why woul you pay 90 dollars for this, they are so much cheaper separately and its Alvin and the Chipmunks

How does Amazon justify charging $80.99 for a bundle of blu-ray movies that cost about a total of $30 if purchased separately?? Am I missing something? Don't believe me check it out for yourself!!! Ice Age Blu ray Digital Copy $11.49 Night Museum Blu ray Ben Stiller $7.99 Alvin Chipmunks Blu ray Jason Lee $10.99 For a total of $30.47. Unless you like giving away $50 for nothing, save your hard earned money and buy these movies separately.
You will be better off waiting until the prices drop on these movies.  The cost is still waaaaaay too high!
